snippet.title: Speakeasy: Last Call Teaser Trailer from Open Late Games
snippet.description:
Official Announcement!
SPEAKEASY: LAST CALL is currently in development. This fan disk is the followup to our popular game SPEAKEASY, featuring side stories and the full soundtrack from the original game. Coming soon.
